---
title: Quick Creamy Penne with PIne Nuts and Peas
description: The simplest way to create a meal that’s fast and easy but still tasty is by focusing on a few thoughtfully paired powerhouse ingredients. In this case, that’s mint for fresh herbiness, peas for a touch of sweet green, and pine nuts for a hint of buttery flavor and crunch. When tossed into this quick, creamy pasta, they create contrasts and combos that feel new with each bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-creamy-penne-67323e08.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/quick-creamy-penne-32c8a398.pdf
